show.description: Wendy was mocked, rejected, and forced into a loveless marriage—until Leo Young crashed her wedding. Once a disfigured outcast, now healed and claimed by the most dangerous man alive, she’s ready to rise. Wild Young Master Son-in-Law is where payback wears a crown and love strikes back.
